Title: 项目概览
Describe: Deep Agents 是一个生产级 AI 智能体运行框架（batteries-included agent harness），基于 LangGraph/LangChain 构建，提供中间件栈、多后端支持和完整的开发工具链
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
项目定位与技术选型

[Description]
Deep Agents 的定位、核心技术栈和解决的问题。基于 LangGraph 的有状态图引擎提供流式执行、检查点持久化和中间件可组合性。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction

package "用户代码" as User {
}

package "Deep Agents SDK" as SDK {
  component "create_deep_agent()" as Factory
  component "Middleware Stack" as MW
  component "Profiles" as Prof
}

package "LangGraph" as LG {
  component "CompiledStateGraph" as Graph
  component "DeltaChannel" as DC
  component "Checkpointer" as CP
}

package "LangChain" as LC {
  component "create_agent" as CA
  component "BaseChatModel" as BCM
  component "BaseTool" as BT
}

package "LLM Providers" as LLM {
  component "Anthropic" as Anth
  component "OpenAI" as OAI
  component "Google" as GG
}

User --> Factory
Factory --> MW
Factory --> Prof
MW --> Graph
Graph --> CA
CA --> BCM
BCM --> Anth
BCM --> OAI
BCM --> GG
Graph --> DC
Graph --> CP
@enduml

[Detail]
**入口点**: `create_deep_agent()` 是整个 SDK 的唯一入口，用户通过它配置模型、工具、中间件和后端。

**核心依赖链**:
- `create_deep_agent()` 内部调用 LangChain 的 `create_agent()` 来构建底层 Agent
- LangGraph 的 `CompiledStateGraph` 提供有状态执行引擎
- `DeltaChannel` 实现增量消息存储，将检查点开销从 O(N²) 降到 O(N)

**设计决策**:
- 选择 LangGraph 而非原生 AsyncIO 是因为需要检查点恢复、流式和持久化
- 中间件架构使得功能可组合、可排除，不同 harness profile 可定制不同的能力集
- 模型无关设计通过 `BaseChatModel` 接口和 `resolve_model()` 字符串解析支持所有主流 LLM

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
生态全景

[Description]
8 个独立版本包的功能划分和关系。每个包独立发布到 PyPI，通过 release-please 自动化管理版本。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction

package "libs/" {
  package "deepagents\n(SDK v0.6.7)" as SDK {
  }
  package "deepagents-code\n(REPL/TUI)" as Code {
  }
  package "deepagents-cli\n(部署工具)" as CLI {
  }
  package "deepagents-acp\n(Agent协议)" as ACP {
  }
  package "deepagents-evals\n(评估套件)" as Evals {
  }
  package "partners/daytona\n(沙箱后端)" as Daytona {
  }
  package "partners/modal\n(云函数后端)" as Modal {
  }
  package "partners/quickjs\n(JS沙箱)" as QJS {
  }
}

Code --> SDK : 精确 pin
CLI --> SDK : 范围约束
ACP --> SDK : 范围约束
Evals --> SDK : 范围约束
Daytona --> SDK : 范围约束
Modal --> SDK : 范围约束
QJS --> SDK : 范围约束
@enduml

[Detail]
**各包职责**:

| 包名 | 版本 | 核心职责 |
|------|------|---------|
| `deepagents` | 0.6.7 | SDK 核心：Agent 构建、中间件、后端协议 |
| `deepagents-code` | — | Textual TUI REPL，交互式开发体验 |
| `deepagents-cli` | 0.1.0 | 部署子命令：init / dev / deploy |
| `deepagents-acp` | — | Agent Context Protocol 服务器实现 |
| `deepagents-evals` | — | 评估套件 + Harbor 集成 |
| `partners/daytona` | — | Daytona 沙箱后端实现 |
| `partners/modal` | — | Modal 云函数后端 |
| `partners/quickjs` | — | QuickJS 嵌入式 JS 沙箱 |

**依赖策略差异**:
- `deepagents-code` 对 SDK 使用精确 pin（`==0.6.7`），确保 TUI 与 SDK 严格同步
- 其他包使用范围约束（`>=0.6.0,<1.0.0`），允许灵活升级
- Partner 包各自独立发布周期，通过 `BackendProtocol` 接口解耦

